(50, 'CCTV to track drains', '2017-11-29', 'I needed my sewer/drains investigated to find exactly where they run under my patio and garden prior to building work. Very proficient and knowledgeable guy. Also, having lifted the manholes, the pipe was several feet down and hard to access, but he managed somehow. Great work and he didn\'t clock watch. Did the job for the agreed price.', 'GU15'),
