(54, 'Water leak traced and repaired', '2019-01-08', 'Steve did an excellent job finding a leak underneath the floor of our utility room. We initially thought it was under the floor of our shower room and Steve had to trace it to its source. He was reassuring throughout and provided top notch service and quality of work. Highly recommended.', 'RH15'),
(55, 'Serivce of boiler', '2018-12-12', 'Came to me promptly, and told me the expansion vessal was faulty, told me to check warrenty, maker came out and fixed at no charge. Then Steve came back and did a proper service at no extra charge a few days later. So EVO Dorking crew saved me a lot of money! Will definately use them going forward. Thanks guys for all your help.', 'RH4'),
(56, 'Power Flush of Heating System and New Pump', '2018-12-10', 'Worked Hard all day from 9.00am to 6.00pm. Radiator system 35 years old at least. Corgi Home Plan engineer was unable to get Boiler working despite 2 visits. Told Corgi would not cover system if blockage was the cause. Colin did the work at short notice and phoned 4 days later to ensure all was well.', 'RH12'),
(57, 'Replaced 3 port valve on hot water system', '2018-11-21', 'I was totally impressed with how Steve works. He quickly located the fault on our boiler after a series of complicated checks. He is methodical in his work and totally dedicated to fault finding. I would not hesitate to recommend Steve and his team for any heating and plumbing work you may have, he is trustworthy and very reliable.', 'RH12'),
(58, 'Previous plumber 2 years ago fitted new combi boiler but left us with terrible \'water hammering\', call to sort it', '2018-10-18', '2nd visit following annual boiler service to sort out severe water hammering that over 2 years previous plumber had not managed to sort out. Steve on first visit made temporary adjustment to stop noise until he returned with parts today to make full adjustment - ecstatic a quiet house.', 'RH20'),
