(61, 'Replaced 2 port valve on hot water system primary circuit from boiler to cylinder', '2018-08-03', 'Was impressed with how quickly Steve picked up on how our rather complicated CH/HW system works, and homed in on the problem. Job completed same day as diagnostic visit. Quite expensive but no complaints - you pay for quality.', 'RH15'),
