(63, 'Fault finding and remedy of thermostatic files (sensing files) as hot water was scalding', '2018-06-12', 'Steve was very methodical in his approach testing all variables to eliminate options in finding the root cause of the problem. Second time I have used EVO and certainly a trusted service provider in my local area based on experience to date.', 'RH12'),
