(66, 'Gas safety check and boiler service', '2018-04-23', 'We have used Steve on numerous occasions, he has also helped out in a crisis and his work has always been satisfactory. We have recommended him to others. We have found Steve to be a very helpful person.', 'RH4'),
(67, 'Fitted new Central Heating Programmer', '2018-04-05', 'Steve has attended on several occasions to repair different jobs at our property. Yesterday was no exception, Steve arrived promptly, worked very efficiently and when the job was completed, left everything neat and tidy. We have also had Steve\'s colleagues attend, if Steve has been snowed under. I wouldn\'t hesitate to recommend, Steve, Harvey or Colin. Many thanks!', 'RH12'),
(68, 'Replace pump, replace 3 way valve, power wash heating system', '2018-03-30', 'Very pleased with the work carried out. Both Steve and Harvey were very polite and professional in their approach to the job.', 'GU15'),
(69, 'Defrost and unblock boiler condensation pipe and restore boiler to full working order', '2018-02-28', 'Our usual boiler service company were not able to attend for 5 days. I rang Steve and he was able to come round that evening (1.5 hours notice) Steve was extremely helpful and polite and gave us full confidence that he would be able to help restore the boiler function. The job was completed quickly and efficiently with tips on how to avoid a future problem. We would definitely recommend Steve and would happily use him again in the future', 'RH12'),
(70, 'Traced and repaired a leaking central heating pipe', '2018-01-19', 'Evo were asked at short notice (emergency leak - water coming through roof) to fix a problem. They responded quickly and fixed the problem on that day. Alongside that they ensured that they made good as much as possible e.G re-laid the carpet as they had to take floor boards up, ensured that no air pockets in central heating etc. Even came back quickly the following day when we identified a minor problem with air trapped in bathroom pipe. Recommended if you are looking for a professional plumber.', 'RH14'),
(71, 'Power flush to central heating system', '2018-01-11', 'Steve and Harvey arrived promptly to Power Flush the Central Heating System, which hadn\'t been cleaned for over 25 years! Copious amounts of black sludge poured out of the system for several hours and was replaced with clean water, special additives were also added to clean the system. When the Central Heating was switched back on, it immediately began operating much more efficiently! My husband and I found when Steve and Harvey had finished, the whole house was left clean and tidy! Many thanks and well done to both, I shall definitely be contacting Steve in the future for any work needed.', 'RH12'),
