(73, 'New Boiler fitted', '2018-01-04', 'Steve diagnosed the problem with my old boiler. We discussed the options and he recommended I contact the manufacturer of my old boiler to see if it was possible to repair it. The manufacturer did not give me any hope that it would be possible to economically repair the old boiler, so I followed Steve\'s recommendation to replace it. Steve responded quickly to get the work done during the cold weather. The new boiler is much better. An excellent job.', 'RH12'),
