(506, 'Hot water cylinder fitted', '2012-08-03', 'Steve was timely, efficient, explained everything. Would definitely have him back', 'RH8'),
(507, 'Gas safety check', '2012-08-17', 'Efficient professional! Having been let down by several other companies it\'s great to finally find a company that can be relied upon.', 'GU7'),
(508, 'Emergency repair to boiler', '2012-10-01', 'Excellent service', 'RH2'),
(509, 'Replaced water tank', '2012-10-03', 'We called Steve out because water was gushing from the loft. Steve came out promptly and solved the problem. We later got him to replace the water tank. We were very happy with the service and found him to be very efficient, reliable and articulate when explaining the problem to us. I have no hesitation in recommending him to anyone looking for a good and friendly plumber', 'RH4'),
(510, 'Emergency plumbing', '2012-10-20', 'We called EVO plumbing out at 9.30 Saturday evening in dire straights! They were with us within 30 minutes. All we can say is, what a really great company. Extremely polite, got the job done without fuss and left us relieved and happy. Great emergency call out rate too, especially considering it was a Saturday night. Can\'t recommend them highly enough.', 'RH12'),
(511, 'Removal of two live birds from behind gas fire', '2012-10-20', 'I found EVO on the internet and they were most obliging. They were very courteous and handled the situation extremely well', 'KT17'),
(512, 'Pre-purchase heating and gas evaluation', '2012-10-25', 'EVO responded rapidly to our query to evaluate the heating and gas systems in a new house and came back with a detailed description the state of the system. We will be using him to fix the problems identified when we hopefully make the move shortly!', 'TW1'),
(513, 'Replaced diverter valve and pump on central heating system', '2012-10-28', 'Steve is a really friendly and genuine guy, helpful with his advise and quick to come out to quote and do the work. A pleasure to deal with, trustworthy and good at his job. Will be using him again for all my plumbing and heating problems. Thanks EVO', 'RH12'),
(514, 'Boiler replacement, general plumbing problems', '2012-10-28', 'Having used EVO Plumbing and Heating on several occasions, we have found Steve to be knowledgeable, reliable and excellent at seeing the job through from start to finish. He is clearly experienced in what he does and works to a very high standard. Would recommend to anyone', 'BN6'),
(515, 'Boiler service and motorised valve change', '2012-11-08', 'Fantastic and professional service. Would thoroughly recommend for their reliability and quality of service.', 'BN6'),
(516, 'Electric boiler repair', '2012-11-14', 'EVO very helpful and provided a top class service repairing my electrical boiler', 'GU15'),
(517, 'New fan and full service on the gas boiler', '2012-11-20', 'Compared to other tradesmen that wee have called out for various repairs to our home, we cannot fault this company at all. Reliable, friendly, honest, professional and the a job well done! We would not hesitate to recommend', 'KT11'),
(518, 'Fixed a non working boiler', '2012-11-22', 'Steve managed to find a very unusual fault with my boiler that was very difficult to diagnose. He saved me having to get a new boiler. He also kept me updated when waiting for spare parts. Highly recommend!', 'RH12'),
(519, 'Gas boiler breakdown', '2012-11-27', 'EVO responded immediately to my telephone call and came out within a couple of hours to assess the problem. New parts were needed and Steve returned the following evening to fit the parts and ensure the house was warm as soon as possible. Really appreciated this kindness. Steve was friendly, efficient and very professional and was able to reassure that the boiler was good for a few more years. I would definitely use this company again. Highly recommend. A huge thank you!', 'RH20'),
(520, 'Repaired leaking heated towel rail and restored pressure in closed heating system', '2012-12-02', 'I was extremely satisfied with the work done and the quick response I received to my call out. The engineer Ross who came out to me on a cold Sunday afternoon was very helpful and courteous and I very grateful to him for the work done', 'RH16'),
(521, 'Service of gas boiler and gas fire', '2012-12-20', 'EVO returned calls promptly and arrived when he said he would. Carried out service work quickly and efficiently and was very pleasant. Will be using him again for the next annual service', 'RH14'),
(522, 'Plumbing work', '2012-12-15', 'Five star company! Worked up to 10pm, did well on a difficult task. Conscientious, responsible and determined.', 'RH10'),
(523, 'boiler breakdown', '2012-12-23', 'What can we say, EVO were fantastic. They came out late on the evening of the 23rd December to try and fix our broken boiler as the insurance cover company was closed, so much for 24hr service eh? Steve was very polite, kept us informed and although unable to fix the problem tonight was professional, articulate and happy to oblige. We wish more trades persons were as brilliant as Steve', 'RH10'),
(524, 'Boiler service and check up', '2016-01-25', 'Would recommend Steve to anyone. Work he has done for me is 10 out of 10! Clean, tidy and very honest.', 'RH10'),
(525, 'Leak under bath repaired', '2013-01-26', 'Throughout the work, the engineer clearly explained what he was doing and the reason for it. It was refreshing to have an engineer who was not rushing the work in order to get on to his next job. He double checked that the issue was resolved and that everything was left in full working order', 'RH12'),
(526, 'Serviced boiler and gas fire', '2013-01-28', 'Very impressed with service and the work, very professional. Steve was unable to keep to the original time as he was running late but he did update me and was with me soon afterwards. Very reasonable price for the work done. I would call him again and would recommend him', 'PO18'),
(527, 'Boiler and gas fire service', '2013-01-28', 'Steve called and updated me as he was running late but arrived soon afterwards. Great job on both boiler and gas fire. Very professional and no mess. I would use Steve again and would recommend him', 'BN1'),
(528, 'Replaced boiler pump', '2013-01-29', 'Called Sunday evening and got an immediate answer. Despite agreeing to work commencing next morning. Stephen called round that evening spending a few minutes for a temporary fix to our lack of heating. The next day he attended as scheduled and fixed the problem to cost and within estimated time frame. Excellent service', 'RH12'),
(529, 'Diagnosis of boiler mate thermal store problem', '2013-01-31', 'I called Steve late one evening after our boiler stopped working. Steve traced the problem to a faulty pump and circuit board. The parts were ordered and repairs made. I found Steve to be very knowledgeable about the thermal store which is a bit of a specialist area as these units are not very common.', 'RH2'),
(530, 'Fitted new circuit board and new pressure switch', '2013-02-01', 'All work was done professionally and efficiently and was explained to me throughout. Steve was very honest, pleasant and courteous', 'GU6'),
(531, 'Gas safety certificate for residential house', '2013-02-07', 'EVO plumbing and heating were very friendly, efficient and knowledgeable. They also managed to come around at short notice. I would certainly recommend them for gas safety certificates.', 'RH4'),
(532, 'Gas leak, faulty fan and gas valve', '2013-02-11', 'We moved into our new home last week with much excitement but found the boiler faulty. Bad luck! I called Steve Morgan of first call for having a look at our boiler. The temperature was around minus 1 degree centigrade. He is excellent in what he does, very focused, professional, dedicated, polite and considerate. He had to put extra effort than it was initially anticipated. We will be giving him a call to change our 20yr old boiler as soon as the winter finishes. It wouldn\'t be fair if I had not given him this feedback. Another important point is, safety comes first in his agenda. I am really grateful to him for the checks he had done on our boiler and shut it down when he found the gas leak. Thanks Steve', 'RH1'),
(533, 'Replaced leaking pipe, services gas appliances, advised on thermostat settings', '2013-02-12', 'Pleasant attitude, very helpful, got the job done. Phoned to follow up that all was OK', 'RH17'),
(534, 'Replace central heating pump and get the system running', '2013-02-14', 'EVO came at very short notice to replace the central heating pump which was situated in a very difficult position under the floor boards. The job took longer than expected but the job was willingly completed', 'RH12'),
(535, 'Clear blocked soil pipe ( 50 meters)', '2013-02-14', 'Work done expertly and efficiently. Drains now in perfect order. Really pleased to have contacted this company. Previously I had an astronomical estimate for this work so I was pleased to have called in EVO! Very satisfied customer! Will recommend EVO Drainage to friends and family.', 'RH10'),
(536, 'Boiler repair and replacement fan.', '2013-03-08', 'Really efficient, came out on a bank holiday Monday to assess the situation, knew what was wrong immediately and returned central heating and hot water to me 2 days later! Very pleased with the service over bank holiday weekend (especially as British gas would take 7 days and power didn\'t come out at all!) thank you', 'RH15'),
(537, 'Central heating boiler locked out, locate cause and rectify if possible', '2013-04-09', 'Boiler locked out Sunday morning. I started to contact heating engineers to try and arrange for the necessary work. Despite being Sunday, Steve Morgan agreed to visit later that day, after he had dealt with some other work already in hand. He arrived around 5 pm, as agreed and checked the various components of the boiler and central heating system. Almost immediately he decided that the problem was not sludge and examined various components, identifying the pump as the likely cause. By then, the previously agreed time and quoted cost had been reached, but Steve was determined to carry on and dismantle the pump, to confirm his diagnosis and attempt to restore the boiler to working condition. Having dismantled the pump, he did find that it was seized and managed to free it by lubricating the spindle. Having reinstalled the pump and restarted the boiler, all went well and the system is still running smoothly the following day. In identifying and rectifying the fault, Steve spent approximately twice the time originally allocated, without any additional charge. Above and beyond indeed. Thorough Steve remained professional and cheerful and was obviously determined to do his best rectify the problem and leave us with a fully functioning boiler and system. I have no hesitation in recommending Steve would be only to happy to re-employ him if the need arose', 'RH16'),
(538, 'Clean radiators and pipework in heating system', '2013-05-06', 'Very conscientious and passionate about his work. Provides explanation as to what the issue is and how the work required reflects on cost. Ensures that work carried out is complete and well done even if it means coming back to make add\' l adjustments. Great work. Would not hesitate to use Steve again', 'RH12'),
(539, 'Toilet cistern and overflow repair', '2013-06-13', 'I contacted Steve just before 5pm and he was at the property within 90 minutes as he had promised. The toilet was fixed very quickly and everything back to normal. Very courteous and prompt service will definitely use again', 'RH14'),
(540, 'Call out to inspect failed boiler', '2013-09-23', 'EVO were very good! I came home to find boiler was broken, called Steve out to look to check. Turns out boiler was still in guarantee and Steve went above and beyond to get it sorted. Got the company to fix it but Steve could have just tried to take the job on himself. If I need anything else I am sure to use him again', 'RH16'),
(541, 'Called to check failed central heating', '2013-10-17', 'The engineer quickly identified the problem and replaced the faulty valve. He was very courteous and helpful. Made sure everything was working perfectly before he left. I have since had to call him for an unrelated repair and received the same excellent service. Will definitely use him again. Have no hesitation recommending him', 'BN7'),
(542, 'Replaced boiler gas valve.', '2013-10-08', 'Steve was very willing to work on my 25 year old boiler. He showed an excellent level of competence and was able to carry out the work in a timely fashion. I had obtained the obsolete part for him to fit. He carefully examined the item before fitting to ensure its worthiness for purpose', 'RH4'),
(543, 'Supply two motorised valves, adjust pipework, replace fan, rewire and service boiler', '2013-10-31', 'EVO\'s engineer very quickly came to a diagnosis of the problem and once the job was started worked extremely efficiently to completion without cutting any corners or taking short cuts. Was polite and cheerful throughout and the finished result was of a good quality standard. I would have no hesitation in recommending his services to others!', 'BN7'),
(544, 'Repair boiler.', '2013-10-30', 'Very happy with the work Steve did. He also checked that the heating was fully functional and safe before he left and also provided advice.', 'RH12'),
(545, 'New Worcester boiler with pipework', '2013-11-06', 'In the pursuit of excellence this young man is a rarity. Nothing is too much trouble to leave everything in order. Courteous and hardworking', 'RH5'),
(546, 'Boiler repair and service.', '2013-11-29', 'Woke up to the boiler not firing up last Saturday. Gave Steve a ring, as we\'d used him before and been impressed with his work. He was able to come round that morning, asses the problem, source parts and fix (including servicing the boiler) before lunch! We have always found Steve to be very reliable, helpful and focused on doing a good job in a customer focused manner. Would thoroughly recommend.', 'RH12'),
(547, 'Disconnect and remove gas hob. Refit and reconnect after kitchen refurbishment', '2013-11-10', 'Every aspect of the work was carried out efficiently and professionally. Steve was always courteous and took time to explain what was happening and give advice as required. I would not hesitate to use this company again in the future', 'RH10'),
(548, 'Fitted new heating pump in airing cupboard', '2013-11-28', 'EVO plumbing and heating able to attend quickly to our call and took no time at all in locating and fixing the problem', 'BN1'),
(549, 'Fitted new central heating pump in airing cupboard', '2013-11-28', 'EVO plumbing and heating able to attend quickly to our call and took no time at all in locating and fixing the problem', 'BN1'),
(550, 'Located a leak under a tiled bathroom floor.', '2013-11-29', 'Highly recommended. Turned up exactly when he said he would. Kept working until the job was complete (23.45). Very satisfied customer. Would definitely use again (but hope I don\'t have to!).', 'RH1'),
(551, 'New gas main', '2014-01-01', 'Gas leak in the bungalow, new supply fitted. To all services. Boiler and heating survey done', 'BN6'),
(552, 'Combination valve  replaced on megaflo and annual boiler service', '2014-01-05', 'Steve was knowledgeable, professional and reliable. I would strongly recommend him', 'RH4'),
(553, 'Bpoiler failure - repair and service', '2014-03-05', 'EVO plumbing and heating were very reliable and courteous. Came on the day they said they would and fixed the problem quickly. I highly recommend this company wholeheartedly', 'TN39'),
(554, 'Boiler service', '2014-03-13', 'Steve completed a service on a boiler that he\'d originally installed. As well as completing the standard emissions and operational checks he reviewed and cleaned a magnetic filter that we have installed. He also helped to review and provide feedback against a quotation we\'d received for a replacement boiler in another property that we own; this was really helpful and outside of the remit of the work that we\'d called on him to complete', 'RH1'),
(555, 'Boiler service and safety check', '2014-03-13', 'Have used EVO\'s services before and as usual were thorough, courteous and professional. Highly recommended', 'RH1'),
(556, 'Replaced boiler', '2014-03-26', 'Great job done! Steve replaced our old boiler, did it thoroughly and kept it all tidy. He was also mindful of the fact that we have small children in the house. Would highly recommend him', 'RH12'),
(557, 'Boiler replacement and new radiators', '2014-03-30', 'Excellent response to call. Excellent non social working, hours willingness. Excellent quality work.', 'RH14'),
(558, 'New boiler fitted', '2014-06-01', 'â€œHighly recommend this company - all work was completed to an excellent standard, very thorough and a pleasure dealing with such a courteous professional company', 'RH13'),
(559, '2 parts on the combi boiler needed replacing.', '2014-06-11', 'Steve was very  polite and gave good explanations of what he had done or needed to do. He was always on time and worked very hard to get our boiler back up and running. We had another problem with the toilet that we asked Steve to look at which he fixed and didn\'t even charge for. such a nice man!', 'RH12');
INSERT INTO `reviews` (`id`, `title`, `date`, `text`, `postcode`) VALUES
(560, 'Boiler repair', '2014-07-25', 'I had a leak from my boiler outside Steve came round the same day and fixed the leak. He then returned to service my boiler and discovered my flue needed replacing. He ordered the part and returned the same week to fit it. Quick prompt service and kept me informed throughout the procedure', 'RH10'),
(561, 'New boiler and a new radiator fitted.', '2014-09-01', 'Steve was very professional, courteous and friendly. Took the trouble to explain what type of boiler was needed and why. Time keeping and tidiness was excellent. No hidden costs. Have no hesitation in recommending him.', 'RH12'),
(562, 'Repair toilet flush.', '2014-10-07', 'Very punctial, Efficient service. Pricing was very fair too, happy to recommend to family and friends.', 'RH10'),
(563, 'Repair to boiler.', '2014-10-17', 'This was a complicated task due to considerable building works going on around the house. Steve was up front from the start with regards costs and even though it ended up taking a lot longer than he had initially expected as it involved replacing more than one faulty component he did not charge us for the extra time. I would thoroughly recommend him and would certainly use him again', 'GU7'),
(564, 'fixed boiler', '2014-10-18', 'Our boiler broke and we called several companies who were very unhelpful, not being able to help for weeks. Spoke to Steve and he came on the same day and fixed the boiler the following day. He was brilliant and honest. Would recommend him to anyone', 'CR3'),
(565, 'Gas heating boiler repair', '2014-11-05', 'Steve Morgan did a great job - he\'s polite professional and cares about his work. There are a lot of plumbers around the Horsham area but I will stick with EVO plumbing and heating. Thank you Steve', 'RH12'),
(566, 'Service gas fire and check flue', '2014-11-10', 'The operative, Steve, called as arranged and went about his job in a very pleasant way. I would recommend EVO very highly.', 'RH17'),
(567, 'Boiler breakdown and repair', '2014-11-20', 'I understood the price before Steve came out, he was more than fair. And to fix my boiler on the spot was nothing but outstanding', 'RH14'),
(568, 'Boiler repair', '2014-11-24', 'Really helpful, nothing is too much trouble, had to return a few times to sort out a few teething problems with our boiler but persevered until it was up and running. Absolutely fantastic. Would highly recommend', 'RH17'),
(569, 'Boiler breakdown and repair', '2014-11-27', 'EVO came out to my boiler breakdown the same day I called him, no call out charges but was quoted a working charge which I thought was fair, boiler up and running within an hour.', 'RH20'),
(570, 'water leak repair under concrete floor.', '2014-11-29', 'I phoned EVO frantically looking for help and the engineer was great. From the first call he was very professional, he was very honest and was superb in sorting out the problem', 'RH20'),
(571, 'Repaired leak on dishwasher connector', '2014-12-08', 'Excellent. Steve identified the problem immediately, fixed it and explained how I could fix it myself in future. As he had finished so quickly, he gave our boiler the once over, gave some advice on it and checked our shower pump and he said if the problem re-occurred, he sort it out at no additional cost', 'GU7'),
(572, 'Soil pipe cleared after blockage', '2014-12-18', 'Prompt service, fair price. The job was dealt with superbly. Harvey took time to clean the area on completion so it would be safe for my children and pet dog. Would recommend.', 'RH10'),
(573, 'Put in new pump for hot water supply', '2015-01-20', 'Really helpful and informative. Five star service from start to finish', 'RH12'),
(574, 'Installing a new programmer for the boiler', '2015-02-03', 'EVOreturned my call. They came out straight away, replaced the programming unit, and got my boiler working in next to no time. Really impressed with his fast, friendly and efficient manner, and the work done!', 'RH12'),
(575, 'System boiler restarted, walkthrough of heating system, checked radiators and performed service', '2015-02-05', 'Very efficient, polite and took time to really explain the system with practical hints and tips for the future', 'RH10'),
(576, 'Repaired leaking toilet cistern', '2015-03-25', 'â€œSteve was able to quickly ascertain what the problem was and fix it. He explained exactly what had happened and what he was doing about it', 'RH12'),
(577, 'Fixing of leaking bath pipes, new taps and hand shower', '2015-05-03', 'Extremely pleased with the work carried out. EVO are a great company and Steve, the engineer,  is a super guy. I will definitely use them again and recommend EVO to others.', 'RH10'),
(578, 'Serviced boiler and checked heating system and controls', '2015-05-15', 'Very happy with the service provided by EVO plumbing and heating.. Good price friendly, tidy engineer. Will use them again.', 'BN1'),
(579, 'Water heaters not working', '2015-06-07', 'Excellent service. Great value. Very competent engineers. Would highly recommend and would certainly use again', 'BN7'),
(580, 'Trace and repair electrical fault on boiler', '2015-06-08', 'Having tried to get in touch with various other companies for over a week - none of which bothered to return my calls, I finally tried EVO plumbing and heating. They answered the phone immediately and told me they could attend the same day! The engineer arrived punctually and resolved a boiler problem at my mothers property that same afternoon! He was totally clear about the price for his attendance and the price for repair work was advised and agreed before he started work. His communication, attitude and helpfulness was totally professional throughout. EVO will be top of my contact list in the future. Highly recommended', 'RH2'),
(581, 'Hot water not working', '2015-06-08', 'EVO\'s engineer came the same day and stayed late to finish fixing the problem. Kept informed exactly what needed to be done and was polite and conscientious. Highly recommended.', 'RH15'),
(582, 'Boxing of bathroom piping after doing trace/repair job', '2015-06-09', 'EVO did another great job after coming back to fix everything that was taken out to do the trace/repair of a particularly tough leak. In short, Steve, the engineer,  managed to succeed where 2 other plumbers had failed! The boxed in area looks great, came in at the right price and was done professionally. Steve went absolutely above and beyond the call of duty (again!) and managed to complete the job beyond satisfaction; absolutely recommended for complete customer focus, utter reliability and top quality of work. Do not hesitate to give this firm a call if you have an emergency!', 'RH6'),
(583, 'Bathroom leakage fixed and washing machine trap replaced', '2015-06-11', 'I have used EVO several times before and once again they provided an excellent service, above and beyond the call of duty. Thanks for a job well done', 'GU6'),
(584, 'Repair on my hot water cylinder.', '2015-06-12', 'Evo were absolutely superb. I had had a couple of other companies come to look at my cylinder and both quoted over the top prices for replacement. Harvey, the engineer from Evo, told me replacement was unnecessary and was able to fix the leaking connection very quickly and at an ultra reasonable price. I am so grateful as I am a pensioner and on limited funds which he fully appreciated. Have already recommended Evo to a couple of friends who have been as impressed as I am.', 'RH1'),
(585, 'Faulty tap repaired', '2015-06-17', 'Excellent service from start to finish. Repair done avoiding complete replacement of tap mixer. Taps now operates as good as new.', 'BN6'),
(586, 'Repair to cold mains pipe.', '2015-06-18', 'Really struggled to find a company prepared to fix an underground mains pipe and at a reasonable price. A fried recommended EVO plumbing, who they had used themselves on several occasions. The stress was taken out of the situation straight away and within 24 hours the repair had been actioned at a price that was very reasonable. Happy to recommend this company to all my friends.', 'BN6'),
(587, 'Reconnect power shower to supply', '2015-06-19', 'Brilliant. Came at short notice to action a critical requirement. Thank you', 'RH16'),
(588, 'Emergency leak fixed late at night', '2015-06-20', 'Prompt service, job well completed, great price, very happy with EVO plumbing and heating. Will use again and recommend wholeheartedly.', 'BN7'),
(589, 'Replace valve and new pipe work in airing cupboard', '2015-07-06', 'Excellent service. I am very pleased with the finished work and the efficiency to which it was carried out.', 'RH1'),
(590, 'Emergency call out to repair a damaged joint between toilet and cistern', '2015-07-07', 'EVO arrived just over an hour after our call. The plumber quickly assessed the problem and looked to see if he could make a quick and easy repair. He quoted a price for the works necessary and this quote was not exceeded. He repaired the problem on the same day and he also used a wet vac to dry out the saturated carpet for which he made no additional charge. At all times he was professional, courteous and kept us informed as to what was going on. As the call was made to an elderly person who used a zimmer frame we were very impressed by his calm and caring approach', 'RH19'),
(591, 'Broken boiler and service', '2015-07-29', 'I would highly recommend EVO. They responded very quickly and Steve, the heating engineer, didn\'t waste anytime and got on with the job. They are reasonable with their pricing and would use them again', 'RH6'),
(592, 'Gas cooker installation', '2015-07-31', 'Very friendly and tidy job. Checked everything thoroughly before they left! Very pleased would highly recommend.', 'RH14'),
(593, 'New boiler installation', '2015-08-07', 'Did what it said on the tin, plus was kind and considerate to my elderly mother in whose house the work was being done.', 'RH20'),
(594, 'Toilet leak fixed', '2015-08-10', 'Prompt service. Arrived same day as called. Very helpful, problem fixed and issue clearly explained and fixed to a very high standard, improving on the original install.', 'RH12'),
(595, 'Replaced taps and toilet siphon', '2015-08-10', 'Excellent service, which was completed quickly and efficiently.', 'RH1'),
(596, 'Fixed leaking toilet', '2015-08-10', 'EVO and Steve, their operative, were excellent from start to finish. Called him 8:30 Monday morning and the work was done by 16:00 Monday afternoon. Faultless customer service!', 'BN7'),
(597, 'Fixing a serious leak in the bathroom', '2015-08-12', 'Excellent - very prompt response, service completed swiftly and with minimal cost. Very pleased', 'RH15'),
(598, 'Repair to bath seal which was leaking', '2015-08-12', 'Fast response and efficient service to rectify fault to bath and radiator (leaking). Work area was left tidy. Very happy with pricing policy too.', 'RH10'),
(599, 'Fixing hot water issue', '2015-08-13', 'EVO heating were  very efficient and kept us up-to-date with the work and costs. We would definitely recommend this company to anyone', 'RH1'),
(600, 'New gas piping to hob', '2015-08-14', 'EVO have completed the job as requested and at short notice so I was delighted with his service. A very pleasant and helpful company to deal with', 'CR3'),
(601, 'New boiler installation and powerflush', '2015-08-30', 'We called out EVO heating to repair our boiler knowing it would need replacing soon. We were given a quotation for a new boiler and following a number of calls we used EVO as they offered us a speedy replacement. The work commenced when they said it would and was completed on time as well. They were careful to ensure that we knew what they were doing and were aware of the progress. The final bill matched the quotation and they were careful to clear and clean everything and to ensure we understood on new installation', 'RH4'),
(602, 'Installation of new gas cooker and removal of old one', '2015-09-16', 'Very high recommendation, excellent work and service. EVO responded quickly to my initial call, and did the job superbly. The plumber even told a plumber related joke. Good work!', 'BN44'),
(603, 'Callout to boiler repair', '2015-11-11', 'I am very happy with all aspects of the service and would happily recommend. Very efficient, stuck to quoted price, and to top it all a great guy.', 'RH4'),
(604, 'Run a new gas line into the house', '2016-12-08', 'Excellent, quick service provided. Quick to come and assess, started the work an hour later. Very happy with EVO plumbing and heating Ltd.', 'BN6'),
(605, 'Repair leaky toilet', '2015-12-14', 'Had difficulty getting any plumber to come out so relieved to have such prompt abd professional service. Did a good job despite difficulties', 'RH19'),
(606, 'Boiler and gas fire. Annual service', '2016-01-04', 'I use this comapny annually because of the great reliable service. On time, polite and very professional, excellent results.', 'RH14'),
(607, 'Replaced our boiler 12 months ago and serviced the boiler this year', '2016-01-13', 'We first called EVO over when we had a gas leak in a home we had just moved into. He came over promptly, checked the house thoroughly, found and fixed the leak. Our boiler then broke down about a month later and again Steve gave us good advice on our options and when we decided to get the new one installed he did a great job. A year later we have just had Steve round to service the boiler and all was well. I would be happy to recommend Steve to anyone on the basis of his service to us', 'RH1'),
(608, 'Hot water running cold.', '2016-01-13', 'Great customer service. Went above what was required of the job. Would definitely use again', 'RH16'),
(609, 'Replace taps', '2016-01-15', 'An all round professional company from start to finish of job. Kept updates with progress and left bathrooms very clean', 'RH20'),
(610, 'New sink vanity unit fitted in down stairs cloak room', '2016-01-22', 'Good workmanship, polite and helpful. Asked him to do work as pleased with previous job', 'RH12'),
(611, 'Remove faulty toilet valve and put new valve in', '2016-01-29', 'Responded to my phone call, made effort to keep time stated. Clean, efficient, friendly and courteous. Other plumbers I phoned didn\'t even respond', 'RH13'),
(612, 'Boiler service supplied and installed kitchen taps', '2016-01-12', 'Always very pleased with the work Steve carries out for me. Prompt, reliable and very friendly. Would highly recommend them', 'RH13'),
(613, 'Repair to leak from valve on pipe in loft.', '2016-02-19', 'First class tradesman, first class job. Very polite and efficient offered explanation on the work required', 'RH6'),
(614, 'Boiler service', '2016-02-23', 'â€œI am delighted to have found EVO. Steve was polite, helpful, efficient. Very reasonable charge for difficult service. I would recommend him to anyone.', 'RH1'),
(615, 'Supply and install new combi boiler', '2016-03-03', 'Excellent job, very polite, efficient, friendly. Quality of workmanship was first class, even provided us with added value by including a remote control thermostat. Thank you.', 'RH12'),
