(915, 'Fixing toilet leak', '2020-10-01', 'Very reliable and did a superb job fixing a leak in a very inaccessible position.', 'RH16'),
(916, 'Fix leak under bath', '2020-10-01', 'Great work. Quick response, polite tidy, and good value. Quality of service cannot be faulted', 'BN6'),
(917, 'Repair to old boiler', '2020-10-01', 'So please we contacted EVO. our usual plumbing company had told us they were unable to get the part needed. Only contacted EVO for a second opinion really, and they were not only able to source the part, but repaired on same day too. We shall be using EVO from now on, not only for their professionalism, but for their honesty and integrity too.', 'RH10'),
(918, 'Resealed shower tray and cleared drainage pipes', '2020-10-01', 'The work was done to a very high standard I would be very happy to use them again.', 'RH12'),
(919, 'Changed the main tap in the kitchen as it was leaking', '2020-10-01', '. Had real trouble finding a plumber.  Nathan was really excellent, very professional and courteous, I would definitely recommend them.', 'TN22'),
(920, 'Change ceramic cartridges on bathroom taps', '2020-10-01', 'So glad we have been able to find a plumbing and heating company that are reliable and happy to take on smaller jobs as well as bigger jobs too. EVO have', 'BN3'),
(921, 'Clear blockage and fix leak from drain', '2020-10-01', 'Very Impressed with all round service. Called early on a Saturday morning and the blocked drain had been cleared and area tidied before midday.', 'RH12'),
(922, 'Cleared badly blocked drain', '2020-10-01', 'EVO were unbelievable.  We had raw sewage spilling over from a manhole on our drive. We struggled to find a drainage company who coud attend same day, but EVO came round literally within an hour of being contacted. Not only was the drain sorted very quickly, but Harvey tidied the entire area before leaving. Brilliant service.', 'RH10'),
(923, 'Replacement of Pump, amendments to pipework and a central heating system flush', '2020-10-01', 'Nathan from Evo Plumbing and Heating was excellent! He worked very hard all day, was updating me throughout the day on progress and what he was doing and finding with regards to the problem on our heating system. He had to get under floor boards but took great care with getting flooring up to gain access and cleared and put everything back as it was found (in fact it was probably a bit cleaner when he left if truth be known!). I would have no hesitation recommending Evo Plumbing as this is the 2nd time I\'ve used them and both times they have been excellent.', 'RH10'),
(924, 'New washing machine valve fitted. Hot valve capped.', '2020-10-01', 'My second time using Evo plumbing . Pleased with the quality of the work done and the friendly, professional young man. Explained what he was doing and cleaned up afterwards. Reasonable price will use Evo plumbers again.', 'GU6'),
(925, 'Clearance of blockage in stack pipe', '2020-10-01', 'The stack pipe in our shared block of flats was totally blocked meaning no one in the block could use any facilities. We we getting desperate as a plumber and another drainage company had not been able to clear the blockage. I called EVO drainage after a personal recommendation and must say they were excellent. The blockage was cleared very quickly meaning we could wash and uses our toilets again.', 'BN1'),
(926, 'First fix of bathroom pipework', '2020-10-11', 'My partner and I have been putting in a new bathroom but wanted a professional plumbing company to do the first fix of all pipework and drainage to make sure it was done properly. EVO were excellent. We approached other plumbers who were either not interested or too expensive. EVO did a superb job, fitting work in around us, and made it vey easy for us to be able to do the second fix and finishing touches ourselves. We will be using EVO again to update our central heating system.', 'BN7'),
(927, 'EVO took out an old shower fitting and fitted a new one and also replaced a dripping tap cartridge and hose', '2020-10-01', 'Punctual, courteous, he completed the work very well and overall my wife and I thought he had a good attitude', 'RH16'),
(928, 'Repair to our worcester boiler', '0202-10-01', 'We had a permanent drip of water running out of our boiler and  had been told by another plumbing company that the boiler needed replacement as it would be too expensive to repair. We had called in EVO to resolve another leak under our kitchen sink, and while repairing this leak Steven from EVO noticed the leak from the boiler. We told him what the other company had said, but Steven was able to remove and repair the part causing the problem. So glad we have found a company who operate an honest and quality service.', 'RH12'),
(929, 'Cleared blockage in kitchen pipe', '2020-10-01', 'Nice neat and tidy work. Punctual and polite. Would recommend them to friends and family', 'RH1'),
(930, 'Replaced central heating pump', '2020-10-01', 'Nathan came out to fix our central heating. He quickly identified the problem and replaced our central heating pump. What really impressed me was how thorough he was, and how he was willing to discuss in depth the different options for sorting out our dysfunctional heating system definitively. Very likely to get work done with them in future', 'RH15'),
(931, 'Shower unit removal and replacement', '2020-10-01', 'Very helpful in setting up appointment at a convenient time. Mark arrived on time, was polite and courteous and completed the work on time and to a very good standard. Faultless :)', 'RH1'),
(932, 'Stop cock and washing machine valve/tap replacement', '2020-10-01', 'Mark ensured that he reached me on the day specified and the work he carried out was of a high quality. This is the second time EVO plumbing has done some work for me and both times they have been very professional, clean, tidy and polite. Recommended.', 'RH2'),
(933, 'Boiler Service and gas safety', '2020-10-06', 'After speaking with Harvey, I told him it was fairly urgent. Not only he accommodated my request, he fitted around my schedule and promptly on time. All specialised equipment was used to carry out necessary checks and Harvey\'s approach and attention to detail was impeccable. I would definitely use them again.', 'KT22'),
(934, 'Leaking drain valve on radiator', '2020-10-01', 'Fast, efficient, tidy, good communications - can\'t fault it really. I shall be using them for all my plumbing and heating requirements from now on', 'RH15'),
(935, 'boiler service and Powerflush 21 radiator heating system', '2020-10-01', 'Our house has always struggled with heating all areas of our house properly. As part of a boiler service, Harvey noticed the water in the system was of poor quality so arranged to powerflush the system 3 days later.  So glad we took his advice. We have now have to turn down radiators that had previously struggled to function at all.  Harvey is one of a team of EVO engineers who have worked at our property. The company is so reliable and all the guys really know their stuff!', 'RH2'),
(936, 'Kitchen sink taps replaced and stabiliser bar fitted under sink', '2020-10-02', 'Mark was very efficient, worked quietly and went out of his way to ensure the work was carried out to a good standard. I have used Evo plumbers before, Steve, Harvey and Mark make a great team. I can thoroughly recommend them.', 'RH16'),
(937, 'Fitted kitchen sink', '2020-10-01', 'Did a great job on fitting the kitchen sink an adapting the plumbing and drainage under the unit. Really professional service. I would recommend them and would use them again', 'GU14'),
(938, 'Powerflush heating system.  Fit magnetic filter and thermostatic radiator valves', '2020-10-01', 'Following problems with our heating system EVO plumbing and heating were recommended to me by another heating company. Nathan arrived and carried out a full assessment of our heating system, including a water quality test that showed the system required a flush.  We now have  a system that is brilliant. There are no longer any cold spots throughout the house and because Nathan fitted thermostatic valves we have the flexibility to easily adjust each room\'s temperature to our requirements. Must say, the service from EVO and Nathan has been excellent.', 'GU14'),
(939, 'Securing outside tap for the autumn/winter', '2020-10-01', 'Mr. Turtle arrived promptly, he knew what to do, and the job was finished very quickl', 'RH2'),
(940, 'Drain clearance and sewage clear up', '2020-10-01', 'Contacted EVO via Checkatrade after finding out my tenants drain was blocked. Needed it resolved ASAP. EVO were able to visit the following day. They were friendly, courteous, polite and, most importantly, sorted out the blockage! The price for the job was reasonable as well. 10 out of 10. Would 100% use again and would definitely recommend. Thank you EVO.', 'BN7'),
(941, 'Plumbing in new gas hob and performing necessary certification', '0202-10-01', 'After being let down several times by another company we contacted EVO plumbing and heating via checkatrade as the number and quality of their review mad them stand out from all others. Work was completed on time and within the agreed price despite it taking longer than originally expected.', 'RH10'),
(942, 'Gas check of oven and hob, replacement of hob and compliance of safety regulations', '2020-11-01', 'British craftsmanship is alive and well. Excellent diagnostics skills. Work efficiently and effectively undertaken', 'RH1'),
(943, 'Fit three new radiators.', '2020-11-01', 'Nathan did a fantastic job. He explained exactly what if he was doing and always asked our opinion if there was an option about how something could be done. He was very polite and knowledgeable, offering us advice about optimum boiler settings, positioning of thermostat and how radiators could be removed for decorating in the future. He did all this whilst remaining COVID-Safe. I would 100% recommend and would definitely use again. Many thanks', 'RH16'),
(944, 'One radiator removed - a new radiator installed in a different place. New thermostats on 5 radiators.', '2020-11-01', 'I was delighted in everyway with the work completed and also with how helpful Nathan was. He kept me fully informed both before the appointment and also on the day. I will definitely be using this company again and would recommend them.', 'GU1'),
(945, 'Changed new taps', '2020-02-01', 'Very happy with tradesmen, very nice.  They worked diligently to remove and replace the taps in main bathroom and en-suite. They were extremely friendly and courteous, and worked to high standards to complete the work.  Would highly recommend', 'CR3'),
(946, 'emergency leak repair through ceiling', '2020-12-01', 'We were very anxious to call an emergency plumber due to our age and the current COVID crisis. Harvey was very aware of our anxieties and did not only an excellent job with the plumbing repair, but also following recommended COVID protocol to make us feel safe and secure whilst he carried out the repair. We are extremely grateful for this.', 'CR3'),
(947, 'Install kitchen tap', '2020-11-01', 'Nathan did a very good job installing my kitchen tap. He always observed Covid restrictions while working. I will definitely be using Evo for my heating and plumbing in the future', 'RH12'),
(948, 'Toilet flush repair', '2020-11-01', 'Called out very late on a saturday evening. All work done well and quietly. Great clearing up afterwards.', 'RH4'),
(949, 'Unblock kitchen sink', '2020-11-01', 'Called at 9.30,arrived within the hour, quickly identified and fixed problem quietly and efficiently. Very good service', 'RH10'),
(950, 'Repair damaged drain at side of property', '2020-11-01', 'We were worried that the drainage repair would be messy and problematic, but needn\'t of worried as the service and quality of work was excellent. Would definitely recommend this company to all others.', 'RH10'),
(951, 'Put new tap in and cleared waste pipe', '2020-11-01', 'EVO were excellent. Very good job, very polite and thorough.  Stephen made good recommendations on a few other plumbing and heating matters that we will be acting on. Stephen was very knowledgeable and gave excellent advice on how we can run our worcester boiler more efficiently.', 'RH20'),
(952, 'Install new soakaway', '2020-11-01', 'We are so grateful to EVO. We had originally employed another company to undertake the work, but were badly let down. After struggling to find another company with the necessary expertise, we contacted EVO drainage following a recommendation from a work colleague. They were professional throughout, and were brilliant for our stress levels. Come highly recommended.', 'GU1'),
(953, 'Replace failing soakaway', '2021-02-01', 'Harvey and his team were absolutely superb. We had had soakaway issues since we moved in to the property 2 years ago. We had had several failed attempts with other companies, but as soon as EVO arrived on site and did their assessment I knew we were in safe hands. The job was not easy because of the garden layout, but EVO managed to replace the soakaway and carry out a full reinstatement, that, within 2 weeks of completion, you wouldn\'t have known any work had been done. British workmanship at it\'s best!', 'RH10'),
(954, 'Survey at rear of property to check for leaking drains', '2021-02-01', 'I have to thank EVO for their honesty and integrity.  Prior to buying our property a survey performed by another company had reported a problem to the sewage foul drainage pipe run at the rear of the property. EVO came round to quote for this work, first performing a survey and drains test to enable them to gauge for themselves the extent of the work. Thankfully the survey and test revealed the drains were not leaking at all. I thank EVO for their honest opinion. Come highly recommended', 'RH10'),
(955, 'Gutter clean town house', '2021-02-28', 'Superb job done at a great price. Had several companies round to quote but were unable to do the job as our house is on 3 stories. Luckily EVO had the right equipment to clean the gutters at high level, and have done a superb job. Have already recommended to both my neighbours.', 'BN1'),
(956, 'Broken pipe to radiator replaced and thermostatic valve installed', '2020-11-01', 'Steve was efficient and fixed the problem. He was careful to explain what needed doing and courteous throughout his visit. Really please with All aspects of the work completed.', 'RH16'),
(957, 'Outside drain blockage fixed', '2020-12-01', 'Fantastic service from Harvey. I called in the evening as I had a blocked drain. I asked for an estimate for the cost of unblocking and was given an estimated range of prices dependent on the work involved. Harvey was able to attend the next working day and did a fantastic job of unblocking the drain and the price was exactly as agreed. Would definitely recommend and will use again in the future. Thank you!', 'RH10'),
(958, 'Remove badly leaking water filter and tap off to avoid further problems', '2020-12-01', 'Phoned Evo at 11am arrived at 3.30 stayed about 1.30 minutes. Contacted this company after other local plumbers unable to help today Mark made a good job and as such would use this company again and would recommend to friends', 'RH16'),
(959, 'Connected 2 water pipes', '2020-12-02', 'The job was completed efficiently. Communication was excellent. Great to have such a reliable company at hand.', 'RH1'),
(960, 'Dripping tap, leaking sing and blocked sink', '2020-12-02', 'Called in the morning, left a message, they called back within the hour and arranged for a plumber to come out about 2:00. Plumber arrived on time and finished the jobs very quickly. Impressed on all counts!', 'RH12'),
(961, 'Replaced two flush valves for two toilets', '2020-02-02', 'Steve and team were  lovely chaps. Reviewed the job a day ago. Managed to source the bespoke parts that were required within 2 days. Came round and fitted them no fuss at all. No issues. Good job done.', 'RH12'),
(962, 'Repairing the taps on the shower fitting (put new taps on) 2nd job the pipe on the wc was leaking', '2020-12-01', 'Charming workforce who were very quick to respond. Came very promptly and just got on with the work. Attitude was very good. Highly delighted with the very neat plumbing work', 'RH13'),
(963, 'The cistern for upstairs wc was continually running, the cistern was taken out, fitted a new syphon in grey plastic and cut out the copper pipework, fitted a new flexible isolating valve connector, re assembled everything', '2020-12-01', 'I would certainly recommend EVO plumbing and heating. Very clean and polite, I used to be a Plumber 65 years ago, we had things in common, we got on very well, tidied up after himself, nothing was too much trouble.', 'RH14'),
(964, 'Leak under bath and basin fixed too.', '2020-12-02', 'Mark was an absolute star. He arrived in the middle of a crisis as we had a leaking pipe. He handled the job very professionally and I felt very sure that he was confident in the job he had to do, there was no fuss and no mess whatsoever. He had to come back and fit a new tap that he had ordered and again was courteous and just got on with the job in hand. Excellent service! Would definitely use the company again.', 'BN1'),
(965, 'Gutters cleaned. Replacement of front section.', '2020-12-01', 'Superb service. Excellent communication throughout, and worked to very high standard in both cleaning and repairing our guttering. They did our neighbours too, and they were also very pleased with the high standard of work. Will definitely use again.', 'BN7'),
(966, 'Repair to heating', '2020-12-01', 'Excellent work performed by team EVO. We had an ongoing heating issue that two other plumbing companies were unable to sort out for us. Steve was able to diagnose and fix the problem vey quickly, and actually charged a lower amount than both the other companies who had been unable to resolve to our satisfaction. Great to have a nice warm house again!', 'TN6'),
(967, 'Replacement of old leaking pipe', '2020-12-02', 'Mark quickly assessed the problem and cut out and replaced the leaking steel pipe with a copper pipe. He also made a couple of very good further recommendations and has now future proofed our system from further leaks', 'RH15'),
(968, 'Replaced a part in toilet cistern', '2020-12-02', 'EVO were aware of our anxiety to get the toilet fixed for our elderly mother and arrived earlier than expected. Diagnosed the problem, got the part from his van and fitted it. Very quick, neat and tidy job. Definitely a five star company!', 'RH10'),
(969, 'Fixed a pipe leaking under the kitchen sink unit', '2021-01-01', 'EVO responded very quickly to our plumbing request. Young man named Steve came round and he was brilliant. He had to saw some of the bottom of the unit away to get to the pipe. He took out two shelves and put it all back and cleaned up after him. Couldn\'t wish for anyone better', 'RH4'),
(970, 'He cleared the side drain as the kitchen sink was clogged', '2021-01-01', 'Great service from EVO. Harvey was very thorough and professional. He immediately found the root cause of the issue and within half an hour resolved a major problem for us. This company come highly recommended.', 'RH10'),
(971, 'Fixed a pipe leaking under the kitchen sink unit', '2021-01-01', 'Young man named Mark and he was brilliant and he had to saw some of the bottom of the unit away to get to the pipe. He took out two shelves and put it all back and cleaned up after him. Couldn\'t wish for anyone better.', 'RH4'),
(972, 'Replacing faulty flush units in 2 toilets', '2021-01-01', 'Really impressive service from Mark. Came the same day I called and kept me updated on timings. Carried out the work very efficiently and just got on with the job. There were a few extra things that needed sorting and he dealt with everything we needed. Would highly recommend and will definitely call again if we need further work carried out', 'RH2'),
(973, 'Restored heating in house', '2020-01-01', 'EVO diagnosed the problem very quickly, and returned the next day  to perform a powerflush. The service and attention to detail was incredible. Our system is working perfectly now. In fact our heating has never worked as well in the 30 years we have lived here.', 'GU11'),
(974, 'Install new soakaway', '2021-01-01', 'Harvey and his team from EVO did a superb job. We\'d endured flooding for years, and even had a couple of guys in previously who hadn\'t been able to sort the issue. From the moment Harvey first arrived on site he seemed to know exactly how to handle the issue, and the results are spectacular. We\'ve had some very heavy rain since the soakaway was installed, and areas that would have previously flooded have remained dry. Such a spectacular difference!', 'BN9'),
(975, 'Blocked kitchen sink and slow draining shower', '2020-01-01', 'Problem solved and they worked late to fit us in on the same day we contacted them. Super service. Highly recommended.', 'RH8'),
(976, 'Fixed leak from pressure release part of the boiler', '2020-01-01', 'Really pleased with the service from Evo, great communication, we were kept informed all the way through. Nathan was polite and helpful, he showed us what was wrong and how he was able to sort it. Will definitely use again.', 'RH10'),
(977, 'Fix fan on boiler', '2020-01-01', 'Tremendous service. Called very late in the day, but Steve came out that evening to diagnose and perform a temporary fix. Came back the next day to change the part. Cannot fault the service and attitude of the company', 'RH15'),
(978, 'Diagnosed hot water issue, fit new valve and actuator, replaced kitchen tap', '2021-01-01', 'Excellent service, happy to recommend. Nathan went well above and beyond in getting everything sorted for us, overcame unforeseen challenges and the results are perfect! Heating, boiler, radiators, water flow, nothing seemed to be a problem for him. House was left spotless after visit.', 'BN6'),
(979, 'Leak from downstairs toilet', '2021-01-01', 'Mark was very proficient. He quickly discovered the issue and was able to rectify the problem to high standard and great repair.', 'RH14'),
(980, 'Fix the central heating/hot water system', '2021-01-01', 'Boiler failed on Thursday. Steve came on Friday and got it working again. He noticed that the pump was leaking. Promised to come back on Monday, which he did. Fitted a new pump, serviced the boiler and repressurised the system. Also showed us how to fix the condensate problem that he had identified. Very friendly and professional service. I would recommend this company unreservedly. Very prompt and timely communications which was much appreciated!', 'RH12'),
(981, 'Leaking shower tray investigated and resolved', '2021-02-01', 'Water stains on kitchen ceiling indicated leaking shower tray above. Called EVO and Mark arrived the next morning. Potential sources of the leak were systematically eliminated and Mark then removed the old silicone around the tray, cleaned up the area and re-siliconed to a high standard. I have used EVO in the past and the high standard of service was maintained.', 'RH16'),
(982, 'New washing machine tap and mains stop cock fitted', '0222-02-01', 'Excellent job carried out by Harvey who turned up at the promised time slot and carried out both jobs very efficiently. Very likeable guy.', 'RH14'),
(983, 'Replacement of faulty ballcock', '2021-02-01', 'Harvey  kept us informed in respect of the appointment and arrived when expected, he replaced the part quickly and efficiently and tidied up after himself', 'RH17'),
(984, 'Repaired leaking toilet', '2021-02-01', 'I use this company all the time, really good service, I am so glad they could come out to me, the man that came is clean and tidy, leaves everything as best he can when he has finished', 'RH10'),
(985, 'Gas check of oven and hob, replacement of hob and compliance of safety regulations', '2021-03-01', 'British craftsmanship is alive and well. Excellent diagnostics skills. Work efficiently and effectively undertaken', 'RH1');
INSERT INTO `reviews` (`id`, `title`, `date`, `text`, `postcode`) VALUES
(986, 'Replacement boiler installed', '2021-03-01', 'My boiler was leaking through the kitchen ceiling last Friday and so I hailed Evo to come to the rescue. Colin was here within half an hour. He inspected the old boiler and presented me with very honest options for repairs, or a new boiler. I decided upon the latter course. He confirmed his quote in writing on Sunday afternoon and Aaron arrived on Monday morning to carry out the work. Initially, Colin had given a time slot of 2 days for the job to be completed. Aaron, however, is a super engineer and all the work was finished in 6 hours. The boiler is a Glow Worm combi, with remote control.', 'RH6'),
(987, 'Resolving a flow issue following work undertaken by another plumber', '2021-03-01', 'Mark was fantastic. He was running a bit late but let us know. He was polite, professional and fixed the problem in no time at all. We would heartily recommend this service. Thanks Mark!', 'SM7'),
(988, 'Boiler leak', '2021-03-01', 'A huge â€œTHANKSâ€ to Aaron today. So so helpful, tidy and professional AND had a great sense of humour! Courteous and polite and diagnosed the problem in minutes. I will be recommending this company to friends and family. Stay safe. Regards Your Lancing customer today', 'BN15'),
(989, 'Boiler fault repair', '2021-04-01', 'I would definitely recommend to family and friends, prompt response and very courteous.', 'RH10'),
(990, 'Replacing faulty fan on boiler', '2021-04-01', 'Aaron answered our emergency call yesterday and fixed our fan today. The service and price was great. Many thanks Aaron', 'RH12'),
(991, 'Dig out broken exterior drainage pipe, replace pipe and rebuild gullies.', '2021-04-01', 'The repairs were carried out by Harvey and Steve who, besides working quietly and efficiently, are two of the most courteous people we have encountered. After completing the work they left the area clean and tidy - even taking the trouble to rake the topsoil level ready for replanting. The finished job is a great credit to them.', 'BN1'),
(992, 'Rebuilt old manhole gully and installed new inspection lid with frame', '2021-04-01', 'Courteous and smooth job. The drains in our house are old and the concrete around one of the gullies was cracking and starting to collapse. Steve and Harvey did a great job of clearing out the drains, jetting to ensure no blockages, and then rebuilding. The concrete work was to a high standard and the new inspection cover looks so much better than the rusty, damaged one we had before.', 'BN7'),
(993, 'Repair leaking cistern, replace kitchen stopcock, replace outside tap', '2022-04-01', 'Work completed by Nathan to time, to budget and efficiently. Update sent with regard to arrival time. Immediate response by phone. Particularly recommended for customers who wish to make an appointment by phone (rather than book anonymously online).', 'GU1'),
(994, 'Installation of 2 new radiators', '2021-04-01', 'We highly recommend Nathan. He is very knowledgeable, thorough, courteous and extremely tidy. We are very pleased with our new radiators. We would be very happy to use his services in the future.', 'RH15'),
(995, 'CCTV drain survey', '2021-04-01', 'I used EVO (Harvey) to complete a CCTV drain survey. I could not recommend him enough. He found out the cause for the drain blockage and advised how to prevent further issues. Great service!', 'RH10'),
(996, 'Fixing a kitchen tap that would not turn off', '2021-06-01', 'Excellent service. New part required and fitted same day. Would highly recommend. Will be using for all future plumbing and heating issues.', 'RH10'),
(997, 'Install new bathroom shower', '2021-06-01', 'We moved into a new build property last Christmas and there was no shower over the bath. Called EVO and Harvey came and priced everything up which with a very competitive quote. Completed the installation of the shower above the bath and fitted new taps within a few hours. He also fitted the shower screen. The work was done to a high standard and the shower is great. He even added extra silicone around the newly fitted shower screen and extra support for the shower rod. Would highly recommend EVO.', 'BN7'),
(998, 'New boiler plus associated work', '2021-07-01', 'Such a good job and such nice people. You can just tell when you are dealing with trustworthy people and these guys are from initial diagnosis to Nathan coming to do the work. He was incredibly polite, tidy, courteous and hard working taking time to explain aspects of the work to a total novice like me. Couldnâ€™t recommend highly enough.', 'RH1'),
(999, 'Repair to leaking pipe joint - Emergency plumbing', '2021-07-01', 'A leak was identified under kitchen sink with potential for serious flooding. EVO Plumbing responded very quickly and within two hours Nathan arrived and quickly and efficiently solved the problem. A very impressive response by a pleasant and cheerful plumber. Very pleased and thoroughly recommend.', 'RH16'),
(1000, 'Replace radiators', '2021-07-01', 'Excellent work from Nathan. Booked a day, arrived on-time, clean and tidy work, all completed as agreed.', 'RH10'),
(1001, 'Boiler repair and service', '2021-07-01', 'Great communication, arrived promptly, very helpful and professional. You have gained a new customer going forward', 'GU6'),
(1002, 'Remove a large radiator and cap off supply at room entry point.Remove a large radiator and cap off supply at room entry point.', '2021-07-01', 'Nathan completed an excellent job today. He de-pressurized and drained the radiator and removed it. He was very knowledgeable about combi boilers and re-pressurized the central heating, checking it heated up properly. Will definitely use this company again.', 'RH6'),
(1003, 'Boiler breakdown and service', '2021-08-01', 'Fantastic The engineer rang to in form me he was 20 mins away Arrived promptly. Extremely helpful. Very nice easy to talk to very knowledgeable. Worked efficiently but not rushing. Very happy', 'GU1'),
(1004, 'Powerflush central heating system', '2021-08-01', 'Nathan from EVO communicated prior to arrival, arrived on the job on time and was thoroughly professional. Nathan carried out his work efficiently and always kept the customer up to date on progress and what he was actually doing ( a font of knowledge). The work has been completed to a professional standard and you can see and feel the difference in our heating system. Nathan completed the job by ensuring he cleaned up after his work and left the premises as he found it. An excellent job and a very happy customer- many thanks, will highly recommend and will personally use again.', 'RH4'),
(1005, 'Gutter clean and repair to Leaking joins', '2021-09-01', 'Harvey did a first class job using hi-tech equipment that allowed him to access difficult to reach guttering. Attention to detail was tremendous, and a really likeable guy.  Highly recommended', 'BN17'),
(1006, 'First, a drainage survey. Then, repairing a damaged sewer pipe', '2021-08-01', 'We are very satisfied with the service provided by EVO Home Services and can only recommend them. Harvey\'s helpful drainage showed that one pipe needed urgent work, so we scheduled for EVO to address this. This repair was done timely and efficiently. Steve kept us informed during the works. The damage was more than expected - there was even a puddle of water at the corner of the house, unable to drain due to a heavily blocked/silted pipe. We were very glad the survey had picked this up and Steve was able to address it. The billing was fair considering the additional work involved. Great Job!', 'RH10'),
(1007, 'PowerFlush of Heating System', '2021-08-01', 'Stephen from EVO communicated prior to arrival, arrived on the job on time and was thoroughly professional. Stephen carried out his work efficiently and always kept the customer up to date on progress and what he was actually doing ( a font of knowledge). The work has been completed to a professional standard and you can see and feel the difference in our heating system. Stephen completed the job by ensuring he cleaned up after his work and left the premises as he found it. An excellent job and a very happy customer- many thanks, will highly recommend and will personally use again.', 'GU6'),
(1008, 'Replacing a kitchen and outside tap, as well as fixing a stopcock.', '2021-08-01', 'We chose Evo as the company have previously completed plumbing work for us and we were very happy with the professional service. Aaron did the work for us and did a great job. He was efficient, friendly, professional and very good at his job, which he clearly takes pride in. We will definitely continue to use Evo when we need any further plumbing jobs done.', 'RH10'),
(1009, 'System Powerflush. filter install and replace 4 radiators', '2021-08-01', 'Very happy with the work completed. Nathan was tidy, professional and did a very thorough job, I would recommend this company', 'RH19'),
(1010, 'Replacing a kitchen tap and outside tap.', '2021-08-01', 'We chose Evo as the company have previously completed plumbing work for us and we were very happy with the professional service. Aaron did the work for us and did a great job. He was efficient, friendly, professional and very good at his job, which he clearly takes pride in. We will definitely continue to use Evo when we need any further plumbing jobs done.', 'RH1'),
(1011, 'Powerflush and balance system', '2021-09-01', 'Stephen was very professional. He arrived very promptly, and worked extremely hard without any breaks. He explained what he was doing throughout the processand cleared up very well at the end. He was polite and efficient.', 'CR3'),
(1012, 'Repair of boiler', '2021-10-01', 'Efficient service, Nathan kept us informed throughout the repair. Very reliable compant who charge sensible prices', 'RH6'),
(1013, 'Service boiler and provide gas safety certificate.', '2021-10-01', 'Lovely, nice and efficient job. Turned up exactly on time, worked quickly and tidily and completed the service exactly as requested. Competitive pricing. Would definitely use again.', 'RH15'),
(1014, 'Replacing boiler and 2 radiators', '2021-10-01', 'Stephen did a great job. He explained clearly what products were available and the different outcomes each would give. This allowed me to choose the most suitable product. He fitted it quickly and efficiently, and cleared up any mess. I would definitely recommend him and will use the company again.', 'RH12'),
(1015, 'Install new boiler and pump', '2021-10-01', 'Stephen was brilliant. Showed up on time, very professional and thorough. Really pleased with this company and itâ€™s nice to deal with a professional engineer. Would definitely recommend.', 'CR3'),
(1016, 'Service and check boiler', '2021-10-01', 'I was very impressed with Nathan he was very polite, very clean got on with the job and also gave me some good advice about my heating regulations things I hadnâ€™t been told about before, so hopefully my bills may be a little cheaper next time. Thank you.', 'GU7'),
(1017, 'Install new boiler', '2021-10-01', 'New boiler installed and system powerflushed promptly-work completed in two days. Engineer Stephen was polite and considerate and kept me informed about the work during the day. He cleaned all areas he had used and the house was left as he found it. An excellent job and I can fully recommend Evo Services', 'RH4'),
(1018, 'To make all the water pipes in an extension to be above ground instead of underfloor', '2021-10-01', 'A very neat job carried out quickly and all the mess and waste cleared up. All done by a very good and likeable plumber at a good price.', 'RH4'),
(1019, 'Remove old combi boiler and replace with new one', '2021-10-01', 'Came to service old boiler upon checking it found it had gone wrong could be fixed but couldn.t guarantee if anything else would after being fixed as 15 years plus old. Agreed on new boiler .Fitted within a week and is much better than old one . Stephen did a great job and does know his stuff .Have used EVO a lot before and very happy with service .Another great job done.', 'RH6'),
(1020, 'Service boiler and balance system', '2021-10-01', 'Nathan turned up on time and did a very good job , explained what he was doing went very will. 5 stars', 'RH4'),
(1021, 'Yearly service carried out', '2021-10-01', 'Stephen carried a yearly service for my boiler and checked my hot water, radiator heating and underfloor heating working in order. He gave me all the advice how I should get the maximum efficiency from my heating system', 'RH10'),
(1022, 'Cleared guttering of debris', '2021-10-01', 'First Class job carried out. Mark took pride in his work and ensured the work was completed t maximum benefit. He used lots of sophisticated equipment that allowed him to access and clean hard to reach places. I would thoroughly recommend.', 'RH10'),
(1023, 'Replace heating pipework after boiler install', '2021-10-01', 'Great service. We kept on getting a pressure drop after we had recently had boiler replaced. Steve was able to pinpoint area of leak very quickly and had us back up and running in no time. Cannot fault any aspect of work from first phone call to work completion', 'RH10'),
(1024, 'Cleared blocked drain', '2021-10-01', 'Came late in the day (at our request) after a very busy day and completed the work quickly and fixed the issue right away. Polite, friendly and first class service.', 'RH10'),
(1025, 'Leaking bathroom towel radiator and replacement waste/plug in bathroom sink', '2021-10-01', 'Mark was responsive on the phone, arrived when he said he would, completed the work and polite and professional throughout.', 'RH2'),
(1026, 'Hitting a new boiler', '2021-10-01', 'My boiler packed up last week and within 5 days I had a new glow worm unit with a 10 year guarantee. From the time I contacted Evo to the time the final checks were made by the most efficient and polite engineer they were nothing but professional, knowledgeable, courteous and hard working. I have used many tradesmen over the last 40 years and Evo are right up there!!!', 'RH16'),
(1027, 'Powerflush our central heating', '2021-10-01', 'Excellent professional service. From the moment I phoned this company I knew these would be the guys for the job. They were knowledgeable over the phone and told me exactly what they would be doing. It was great, also that they were able to one hundred percent deliver on what they had said - the difference to our heating system is absolutely staggering. Great tem!', 'BN1'),
(1028, 'Gutter Clearance', '2021-10-01', 'Fantastic work. Friendly, polite and good rates. Arrived right on time and were kept up to date with progress too.', 'BN6'),
(1029, 'Repair leaking toilet and faulty tap', '2021-10-01', 'Very quick response to an urgent job. Friendly and very fair price', 'RH10'),
(1030, 'Install new boiler', '2021-10-01', 'All work very professionally done. Excellent job carried out, tidy, clear communication of the process. Very pleasant.', 'BN7'),
(1031, 'Put in a new Saniflo - commissioned and tested', '2021-12-01', 'He was absolutely brilliant, really good. Very polite, very clean and tidy. Would definitely recommend him.', 'CR6'),
(1032, 'Sorted problem with overflowing drain', '2021-12-01', 'Our drain overflowed yesterday and we had to deal with a pretty nasty mess. We called EVO plumbing and they came out early afternoon. Harvey was our technician and he was amazing! Prompt, professional, and courteous. He cleared our drainage issue in about 30 minutes and cleaned the area when he finished.', 'RH12'),
(1033, 'Fix Leak and service boiler', '2021-10-01', 'We were very grateful to get a quick response and resolution to our leaking boiler. We made this appointment at very short notice and were very happy with the friendly service and very reasonable charges', 'BN1'),
(1034, 'Install new boiler and system filter', '2021-12-01', 'Brilliant service, very friendly and efficient. Job was completed quickly and well. No mess. Highly recommend', 'BN6'),
(1035, 'CCTV drain survey with report and recordings', '2021-12-01', 'EVO were quick to respond and provided a clear and concise report with the survey results. Harvey was brilliant, I was with him when the survey was first performed and he gave an in depth explanation and solution to everything that he found. The cost was very reasonable too, far lower than other companies were quoting for this work.', 'BN6'),
(1036, 'Clean Pation at rear of property', '2021-01-01', 'The results are absolutely stunning. Harvey worked very quickly and his attention to detail was superb. We are absolutely over the moon with the results, the patio looks just like it did when it was first put in.', 'RH17'),
(1037, 'Boiler Fix', '2022-01-01', 'A timely fix to get heat back on for the weekend. Steve was superb from first contact through to job completion. He was able to come out and diagnose and fix the boiler all on the same day. Very reasonable charges too.', 'TN6'),
(1038, 'Emergency leak repair', '2022-02-01', 'Very Grateful to EVO for the quick turnaround. Called late afternoon and problem sorted within two hours of first contact.', 'RH10'),
(1039, 'Boiler service and repair', '2022-02-01', 'First time using EVO. Engineer Nathan was knowledgeable, personable and extremely helpful. Would definitely recommend.', 'RH12'),
(1040, 'Boiler service and repair', '2022-02-01', 'Really efficient, friendly service. Quick turnaround when booking the service, good communication and reliable. Service and advice was thorough and comprehensive.', 'KT22'),
(1041, 'Replaced pump and fitted new thermostats to some radiators', '2022-02-01', 'Harvey was very efficient, knowledgeable and explanatory. He left his work areas tidy and clean. Highly recommend.', 'BN7'),
(1042, 'Boiler and Megaflow service', '2022-02-01', 'Can\'t fault any aspect of the service. They were punctual. friendly, knowledgeable, and will use again.', 'RH10'),
(1043, 'Fix gutter connection to underground drainage', '2022-02-01', 'Great Communication, reliability and pricing. Very warm, friendly service too', 'RH10'),
(1044, 'Home buyer drain survey', '2022-02-01', 'Highly recommend. They were very flexible to work to our timescales and produced an excellent report that was easy to understand.', 'RH10'),
(1045, 'Powerflush heating system and fit magnetic filter.', '2022-02-01', 'Super service by Steve and Aaron from EVO. They diagnosed the cause of our heating issues and acted quickly. We now have heating fully working in every room for the first time in years. The results were truly spectacular!', 'RH10'),
(1046, 'Repair leaks on boiler system', '2022-02-01', 'Many thanks to team EVO. They responded swiftly and worked conscientiously to rectify problems from install work carried out by another local firm. Great that they could turn this round so quickly for us.', 'GU1'),
(1047, 'unblock a toilet', '2022-02-01', 'Quick and thorough service. A toilet rim block and a previous plumber\'s drain rod rubber plunger were successfully removed.', 'RH10'),
(1048, 'Cylinder, tank and sundries replacement', '2022-02-01', 'During the past week Steve and co. Have made several visits for differing plumbing problems. Their work on every task has been excellent. I have already booked them for a boiler replacement', 'RH6'),
(1049, 'Repair to toilet', '2023-03-01', 'This job was very well executed. Itwas an awkward job involving replacing the filler valve in a cistern. Difficult to reach. Mark sourced the part and fitted the new valve. He also connected a tap on some flexi hose so that the water could be cut off to the cistern without shutting the whole house down. Mark is a friendly and very competent workman.', 'RH6'),
(1050, 'Water leak from immersion cylinder', '2022-03-01', 'Contacted EVO in the morning and Mark (plumber) came out at about 5pm and fixed the leak within the hour.', 'RH12'),
(1051, 'Boiler service and central heating check', '2022-03-01', 'Really pleased with Aaron from Evo completing a standard boiler service. They were able to visit the same week I made the enquiry and were quick to reply. Very friendly and polite and gave some very honest and practical advice without and â€˜upsellingâ€™. Highly recommend and will definitely use them again.', 'RH10'),
(1052, 'Annual service for unvented cylinder system Verified Review', '2022-03-01', 'Stephen did a super job as always. 100% recommend', 'RH12'),
(1053, 'Diagnose noise and replace valve', '2022-02-01', 'First class - kept us informed about when he would arrive. Found the problem straightaway, obtained spare part and fitted. Worked neatly and successfully.', 'BN6'),
(1054, 'Fix leak in en-suite bathroom', '2022-02-01', 'Top rate service. Acted very quickly, arriving within an hour of call, which was great as I had water dripping through a downstairs light fitting. Spent time after fix helping me clear up which was greatly appreciated.', 'RH2'),
(1055, 'Powerflush heating system to resolve boiler error and restore heat', '2022-02-01', 'Steve from EVO plumbing and heating did a fantastic job. He managed to resolve a boiler fault previously reported by another engineer, and also restored our heating to a level way beyond what we previously had. We had a powerflush done by another company several years ago. EVO were slightly more expensive but the difference in equipment used and improved results are totally incomparable.', 'RH10'),
(1056, 'Installing a new boiler', '2022-02-01', 'Stephen installed a new boiler for us. His work was of excellent quality, he was extremely tidy and friendly and took the time to explain how everything worked and answered all of my questions. Excellent worker. I would highly recommend him.', 'RH12'),
(1057, 'Install waste disposal unit', '2022-02-01', 'Great work. Friendly and dependable service. Will definitely be calling again for further work', 'TN6'),
(1058, 'Trace and fix leak', '2022-02-01', 'Terrific responsive local service. Called on a Sunday and issue was resolved within 2 hours', 'TN7'),
(1059, 'Repair a leaking pipe', '2022-02-01', 'Evo returned my call quickly and a plumber was with me within an hour. He was polite, efficient and tidy. I would be glad to use Evo again.', 'RH1'),
(1060, 'Reduced length of time for hot water to come out of taps', '2022-02-01', 'Second time I have used EVO plumbing and heating and second time I have been really impressed. Highly recommend', 'RH6'),
(1061, 'Basin cleared from blockage', '2022-02-01', 'Harvey was very efficient and the job was completed quickly and well. Charges were much more reasonable than other companies I phoned.', 'RH10'),
(1062, 'He serviced my boiler and replaced a part', '2022-02-01', 'Steven was excellent, he arrived early and fitted us in before my hospital appointment. Would absolutely recommend this company.', 'RH4'),
(1063, 'Boiler service and gas safety check', '2022-02-01', 'Excellent professional service delivered, a pleasure to deal with from start to finish - would definitely use again.', 'RH13'),
(1064, 'Perform home buyer CCTV drain survey', '2022-04-01', 'Copuld not be more delighted with the service received from Harvey at EVO drainage. They responded quickly to our enquiry - we were up against a tight deadline so very much appreciated. We received the report which was clear and concise and very easy to follow, Will be using their plumbing and heating division when we are in the new property', 'TN6'),
(1065, 'To supply and fit radiators', '2022-04-01', 'The work was carried out by Steven, who was extremely helpful and considerate He performed all the work to a very high standard and we are very pleased with the result. We would not hesitate in recommending the company to anyone requiring central heating work.', 'TN22'),
(1066, 'Boiler inspection and resolve pressure issue', '2022-04-01', 'Brilliant professional and reliable service.', 'RH17'),
(1067, 'Replacement of Leaking taps', '2022-04-01', 'Work very efficiently on all work carried out. Would recommend.', 'KT22'),
(1068, 'Pre purchase drain survey', '2022-04-01', 'Really pleased with the service. Harvey bent over backwards to accommodate us before contract exchange. The CCTV survey report was produced very quickly after the survey and was clear and concise. Will definitely use again for further plumbing and heating work once the purchase is complete', 'BN1'),
(1069, 'Boiler inspection and resolve pressure issues', '2022-04-01', 'Brilliant professional and reliable service.', 'RH12'),
(1070, 'Investigated boiler problem and installed new boiler', '2022-04-01', 'Fantastic service, our boiler broke down on a Sunday morning, our usual engineer couldnâ€™t get out to us but contacted Evo who organised an engineer for the next day. They got the boiler working but it needed repairs. Evo quoted for the work plus the cost of a new boiler. Made sense to get a new boiler, this was installed within a week. Really pleased with the workmanship and service provided', 'RH13'),
(1071, 'Dealt with a toilet blockage.', '2022-04-01', 'He rang me to ask details. When he arrived he was able to get to the root of the problem. All the time he was courteous and professional. The blockage in the toilet was fixed quickly and competently. I would certainly think of using this firm again if needed.', 'RH1'),
(1072, 'Central heating - gas boiler service', '2022-04-01', 'Nathan came to service our gas central heating system today. He was very friendly and knowledgeable. He clearly explained everything he was doing as he went and completed all remediation work while he was here. We received the gas safety certificate before he had even left our house which was great. We will definitely be using Nathan /EVO again. Thank you very much', 'RH6'),
(1073, 'Install outside tap', '2022-04-01', 'Very happy with the work. The workman was very friendly and the work was done neatly too, with no mess.', 'TN6'),
(1074, 'Install new shower', '2022-04-01', 'Great work throughout. Very easy to communicate with. Went along with their choice of shower and really glad I followed their recommendation as it\'s superb!', 'RH10'),
(1075, 'Boiler service and central heating check', '2022-04-01', 'As ever I am completely happy with Stephenfrom Evo Plumbing, Heating and Drainage. Always pleasant, prompt, efficient and helpful. I wouldn\'t dream of using any other plumbing company. This visit was a routine service but I have had several other issues which have also been dealt with by Evo and I would not hesitate to recommend them to anyone.', 'GU7'),
(1076, 'Boiler repair', '2022-04-01', 'Great work by these guys. Steve was able to more or less diagnose the problem over the phone before coming to us, allowing him to fix and totally resolve the problem on first visit', 'TN6'),
(1077, 'Patio and driveway cleaned', '2022-04-01', 'The transformation is absolutely amazing. Job was completed competently and quick time and with great care.', 'RH4'),
(1078, 'Replacement of kitchen mixer tap.', '2022-04-01', 'Excellent service! Mark came the day after our request for a plumber and was very pleasant and gave an efficient service. No mess, everything cleared up after the work. Would thoroughly recommend and use again. Many thanks.', 'RH6'),
(1079, 'Annual biler service', '2022-02-01', 'This was the second year we have used EVO for our annual boiler service and we\'ll continue to do so. Very easy to make the booking via phone. Nathan, the engineer arrived on time, was very friendly, knowledgeable and tidy. Very easy online invoice and Gas Safety Certificate issued. Will def use again.', 'CR3'),
(1080, 'CCTV survey and root removal', '2022-04-01', 'Called Harvey at EVO drainage to investigate why pour drains kept on blocking. Harvey was able to investigate and resolve very quickly and at a very fair price.  Would definitely recommend', 'BN7'),
(1081, 'Gutter clean', '2022-04-01', 'Such great service. Our property has  a lot of gutters that are hard to access, but using specialist equipment Mark was able to clear all of these places. He took great pride in his work and we would highly recommend him.', 'BN7');
